title: What are the most well known song titles that don’t occur in the song lyrics? - Quora

response.answer_text: I can think of so many. Unfinished Sympathy- Massive Attack Blue Monday - New Order The Weight - The Band Iris - Goo Goo Dolls Sympathy for the Devil - Rolling Stones Brain Damage - Pink Floyd Subterranean Homesick Blues - Bob Dylan Digital Love - Daft Punk Smells Like Teen Spirit - Nirvana How Soon is Now - The Smiths A Day in the Life - The Beatles Blood on the Motorway - DJ Shadow Baba O’Reilly - The Who Space Oddity - David Bowie Smalltown Boy - Bronski Beat Cherub Rock - Smashing Pumpkins Paranoid Android - Radiohead Lullaby - The Cure Fairytale of New York - The Pogues Basket Case - Green Day Rapper’s Delight - Sugar Hill Gang Death on the Stairs - The Libertines Professional Widow - Tori Amos Empire State of Mind - Jay Z Porcelain - Moby Cloudbusting - Kate Bush 1983… (A Merman I Should Turn to Be) - The Jimi Hendrix Experience Fade to Black - Metallica L.S.F - Kasabian Clint Eastwood - Gorillaz Venus in Furs - Velvet Underground Breakfast in America- Supertramp Christmas Card from a Hooker in Minneapolis- Tom Waits Probably everything by Underworld. To be fair it wouldn’t be unreasonable to assume Underworld choose song titles by closing their eyes and stabbing a pin in a newspaper. Ok, I’m going to stop now .

I hope you all enjoy reading/listening/watching as much as I do posting these: 40 - U2  A Day in the Life - The Beatles  Baba O'Riley - The Who  Big Empty - Stone Temple Pilots  Big Log - Robert Plant  Black Dog - Led Zeppelin  Bohemian Rhapsody - Queen  Breakfast in America - Supertramp  Epic - Faith No More  For What It's Worth - Buffalo Springfield  Heavy - Collective Soul  Interstate Love Song - STP  Iris - Goo Goo Dolls  Jacob's Ladder - Rush  Love Song - Tesla  Maggie May - Rod Stewart  Miami 2017 - Billy Joel  Over the Hills and Far Away - Led Zeppelin  Paranoid - Black Sabbath  Plush - STP  Space Age Love Song - A Flock of Seagulls  Teen Angst - Cracker  Tempus Fugit - Yes  The 59th Street Bridge Song - S & G  The Breakup Song - The Greg Kihn Band  The Spirit of Radio - Rush  Tubthumping - Chumbawamba  What's Up - 4 Non-Blondes  Won't Get Fooled Again - The Who  Young Turks - Rod Stewart
